<div class="home-body">

  <div class="banner text-center">
      <%= render 'shared/navbar' %>
      <div class="banner-title">
        <div class="banner-content text-center">
          <h1>Making Tutoring Uncomplicated</h1>
          <p>Young enthusiastic tutors, no agency fees and competitive prices</p>
          <div class="enquire">
            <button type="button" class="btn enquire-button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#contactModal">Enquire</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#home-page-tutors-block" class="chevron-down">
          <i class="fa fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </a>

      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tutors text-center" id="home-page-tutors-block">

    <h3>Our Tutors</h3>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row" style="overflow: hidden">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
          <div class="home-page-tutor-section">
            <div id="map1" style="height: 250px; width: 100%"></div>
            <div class="tutor-bottom-section">
              <div class="short-details text-center">
                <img src="assets/FullSizeRender.jpg" class="avatar" id="nickphoto"  style="height: 150px; width: 150px">
                <div class="short-details-title">
                  <h4 class="tutor-name">Nicholas Lagnado</h4>
                  <p class="institution-title">University of Bristol (2014-2017)</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">Economics and Philosophy (BSc) – 1st Class Honours</p>
                  <p class="institution-title">Latymer Upper School</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">A-Levels – Economics (A*), Philosophy (A*), Maths (A), Spanish (A)</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">GCSEs  – 9 A*s, 2 As</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tutor-quote">

                  <p>I am a recent Graduate from the University of Bristol who has experience tutoring students from a variety of different levels, ages, and backgrounds. I enjoy simplifying and articulating complex ideas and the rewarding aspect of teaching others. Outside of the classroom I am an avid tennis enthusiast and have experience coaching children.</p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
          <div class="home-page-tutor-section">
              <div id="map2" style="height: 250px; width: 100%"></div>
              <div class="tutor-bottom-section">
              <div class="short-details text-center">
                <div class="avatar" id="hamishphoto">
                  <img src="assets/headshot.jpg">
                </div>
                <div class="short-details-title">
                  <h4 class="tutor-name">Hamish Hall</h4>
                  <p class="institution-title">University of Oxford (2014-2018)</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">Engineering Science – 1st Class Honours currently</p>
                  <p class="institution-title">Latymer Upper School</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">A-Levels – Maths (A*), Further Maths (A*), Physics (A*), Chemistry (A*), English Lit. (A*)</p>
                  <p class="institution-details">GCSEs  – 10 A*s, 1 A</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tutor-quote">

                <p>I am a recent Graduate from the University of Bristol who has experience tutoring students from a variety of different levels, ages, and backgrounds. I enjoy simplifying and articulating complex ideas and the rewarding aspect of teaching others. Outside of the classroom I am an avid tennis enthusiast and have experience coaching children.</p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="tutors" class="btn tutors-button">Read More</a>

  </div>

</div>


<div id="contactModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
  <%= render 'shared/contact_modal', email: @email %>
</div>

